00:01:51.000 --> 00:01:55.000
[Amit Varma]: Rebel Sultans by the young historian Manu Pillay.

00:01:55.000 --> 00:01:58.000
[Amit Varma]: Manu is only 28 years old and has already written two books,

00:01:58.000 --> 00:02:00.000
[Amit Varma]: The Ivory Throne and Rebel Sultans,

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:04.000
[Amit Varma]: and his writing is exactly what good history should be.

00:02:04.000 --> 00:02:07.000
[Amit Varma]: Lucid, easy to read, witty and very, very entertaining.

00:02:07.000 --> 00:02:10.000
[Amit Varma]: This is clearly a man in love with his subject.

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:12.000
