00:56:23.400 --> 00:56:28.440
[Amit Varma]: Shah is sort of looking at his legacy and building up all of this cultural whatever.

00:56:28.440 --> 00:56:31.400
[Guest]: Building up cities and now Amit Shah also builds up his own new city.

00:56:31.400 --> 00:56:36.800
